{"title":"SSH超时问题","date":"2020-10-20T02:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年10月20日","L":"2020/10/20","MM-DD":"10-20"},"link":"2020/10/20/SSH超时问题","tags":["网络"],"categories":["学习"],"updated":"2021-11-30T02:03:56.274Z","content":"<p>新电脑提交github时报超时，本来以为公司网络问题，经过查询得知可以切换端口解决</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ ssh -t git@github.com</span><br><span class=\"line\">ssh: connect to host github.com port 22: Connection timed out</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"测试端口可用性\">测试端口可用性<a title=\"#测试端口可用性\" href=\"#测试端口可用性\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ ssh -T -p 443 git@ssh.github.com</span><br><span class=\"line\">Connection reset by 20.205.243.160 port 443</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"编辑-~/.ssh/config-文件\">编辑 <code>~/.ssh/config</code> 文件<a title=\"#编辑-~/.ssh/config-文件\" href=\"#编辑-~/.ssh/config-文件\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Host github.com</span><br><span class=\"line\">Hostname ssh.github.com</span><br><span class=\"line\">Port 443</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>再次测试</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ ssh -t git@github.com</span><br><span class=\"line\">Connection reset by 20.205.243.160 port 443</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>###参考<br>\n<a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/troubleshooting-ssh/using-ssh-over-the-https-port\" target=\"_blank\">Using SSH over the HTTPS port</a></p>\n","next":{"title":"Spring事件监听机制","link":"2020/09/10/Spring事件监听机制"},"plink":"https://zinki.github.io/2020/10/20/SSH超时问题/","toc":[{"id":"测试端口可用性","title":"测试端口可用性","index":"1"},{"id":"编辑-~/.ssh/config-文件","title":"编辑 ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;config 文件","index":"2"}]}